name: BillytheRandomNumberGoat
0:
”Alexa ask Billy Goat for a number.”
”Alexa ask Billy Goat, what's my random number?”
”Alexa ask Billy Goat, give me a number between five and twenty.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: billy goat
des: Billy the Random Number Goat will provide you with a random number. If you ask Billy Goat for a random number or ask "What is my random number?", Billy Goat will return a random number between one and one hundred. You can also ask Billy Goat for a random number between a specific range. Simply ask Billy Goat to give you a number between one and ten or five and thirty. It's that simple!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
